---

import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '@/styles/globals.css'
import miro_portrait from "@/components/portrait_miro.jpg"
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import SocialMedia from '@/components/SocialMedia.astro';
---

<Layout title="Miro Wilms">
	<Image src={miro_portrait} alt="Miro Portrait" class="rounded-full w-28 h-28" />
		<div class="leading-relaxed my-8 space-y-4">
			<p>
				I am a self-taught technologist with a deep passion for building products that make a real difference. My journey has taken me from hands-on software development to founding and scaling a SaaS startup, leading engineering, product and commercial teams, and now to my current role as an AI Lead.
			</p>
			<p>
				I believe AI is the foundational technology of our lifetime. In my work, I help organizations unlock the true potential of AI—solving bottlenecks and driving meaningful impact with technology that is ready today. At the same time, I am deeply aware of the risks and challenges that come with powerful new tools. I am committed to promoting responsible, risk-conscious AI adoption and contributing to the broader conversation around AI safety.
			</p>
			<p>
				I am always interested in supporting projects with positive impact—whether as an advisor or in a hands-on capacity—particularly those at the intersection of AI, responsibility, and safety.
			</p>
		</div>
		<SocialMedia />
</Layout>
